      "output": "[Line 742]: [13/05/2024, 17:38:04] Marquis A. Caines (BYPCardiff): No worries. I�?Tm hoping you can raise some capital\r\r\n[Line 1732]: [03/06/2024, 10:41:38] Andie: Cant wait to pour some capital behind ur brands\r\r\n[Line 1854]: Ignite your journey to success at the third annual Birmingham Black Business Show �?\" a magnetic force shaping careers and fostering connections. This isn't just an event; it's a gateway to growth, opportunity, and a vibrant community of Black professionals, business owners and driven entrepreneurs.\r\n[Line 2035]: [04/06/2024, 17:23:57] Marquis A. Caines (BYPCardiff): I think there�?Ts a balance. A healthy balance between social entrepreneurship and capitalism\r\r\n[Line 2594]: If you know any African founders and startups that are raising capital and would like to pitch to angel investors, please share this with them and have them email me at babiolu@venturehue.com to request a nomination and I will send them the application form to apply for the showcase.\r\r\n[Line 2758]: [10/06/2024, 11:46:24] Andie: Especially in human capital! Cause ur boy is still building up the dough �Y~' �?Z<This message was edited>\r\r\n[Line 2923]: [10/06/2024, 14:37:10] Andie: cause theres lots of red taping with this stupid gov atm\r\r\n[Line 3003]: [10/06/2024, 14:46:08] Marquis A. Caines (BYPCardiff): They�?Tre raising capital?\r\r\n[Line 3130]: [10/06/2024, 18:58:32] Andie: So I was like yeah make sense is only Wales and the most activity is in Cardiff Capitol region\r\r\n[Line 3227]:    - **Integration Needs**: Any third-party services or APIs that need to be integrated?\r\n[Line 3317]:    - **Integration Needs**: Any third-party services or APIs that need to be integrated for each venture?\r\n[Line 3479]: [10/06/2024, 19:18:31] Marquis A. Caines (BYPCardiff): I only say this because America is building rapidly\r\r\n[Line 3481]: [10/06/2024, 19:18:39] Marquis A. Caines (BYPCardiff): And raising capital from\r\n[Line 3485]: [10/06/2024, 19:19:00] Marquis A. Caines (BYPCardiff): Innovation and tech is stifled because of capital\r\r\n[Line 3487]: [10/06/2024, 19:19:08] Marquis A. Caines (BYPCardiff): If we decrease the required capital\r\r\n[Line 3808]: [10/06/2024, 20:07:31] Andie: Thats escapism for the mind tho\r\r\n[Line 4116]: [11/06/2024, 06:57:21] Marquis A. Caines (BYPCardiff): There�?Ts a lot of capital between Bristol and wales\r\r\n[Line 4551]: CAPITOL CENTRE, UNIT 3 QUEEN ST, CARDIFF CHIO 2HQ\r\n[Line 5222]: [26/06/2024, 07:30:20] Marquis A. Caines (BYPCardiff): But still can�?Tt raise capital\r\r\n[Line 5553]: [26/06/2024, 09:10:08] Andie: is more complex and not directly supported via official APIs.\r\r\n[Line 5554]: [26/06/2024, 09:10:25] Andie: API, Application Programming Interface\r\r\n[Line 5555]: [26/06/2024, 09:10:37] Andie: WhatsApp's official API through Twilio (or any other provider) does not provide admin functionalities such as kicking users from groups.\r\r\n[Line 5556]: [26/06/2024, 09:10:43] Andie: This level of control is typically reserved for the WhatsApp application itself and is not exposed through third-party APIs due to security and privacy concerns.\r\r\n[Line 5772]: [27/06/2024, 07:41:28] Andie: Wow! Honestly i wonder how entrepreneurship and raising capital there is like\r\r\n[Line 6925]: [16/07/2024, 09:21:13] Sharonita Kostini: Oh the code for the Capitol door is 0724 and press enter. The doors shut at 8pm so save it to pass around to your friends so they can enter if they arrive late.\r\r\n[Line 7742]: [30/07/2024, 10:28:47] Marquis A. Caines (BYPCardiff): Founder wise: what are your greatest struggles, other than capital?\r\r\n[Line 7770]: [30/07/2024, 12:52:40] Andie: it is a capital city after all, that's what I think all the times, but definitely I think the people moving in have drove up the prices but also the economy downturn which as put everyone into a different mindset in terms of letting out accomdations\r\r\n[Line 7815]: [30/07/2024, 15:53:46] M