erpowers. Your season of preparation in the wilderness is over. Now is the time to begin the work.\r\r\n[Line 8714]: The Scripture Mirror: Matthew 7:3-5 - \"Why do you look at the speck of sawdust in your brother's eye and pay no attention to the plank in your own eye?... first take the plank out of your own eye, and then you will see clearly to remove the speck from your brother's eye.\"\r\r\n[Line 8723]: [27/10/2025, 23:15:21] Hope: The chaos was very peaceful, no one said things they don�?Tt mean. He understands my perspective i understand his\r\r\n[Line 8734]: [27/10/2025, 23:20:16] Andie: \"He understands my perspective, I understand his.\" This is evidence of empathy and mutual submission (hypotass�?). Even in disagreement, they were \"arranging themselves under\" the higher principle of trying to understand each other.\r\r\n[Line 8792]: [27/10/2025, 23:32:11] Andie: God said to *Tell him this:* 'I need a partner who, especially when things are hard, will run toward God with me, not away from Him.' His response to that statement will tell you everything you need to know.\"\r\r\n[Line 8826]: [27/10/2025, 23:39:56] Andie: He is bringing this pattern to the surface not to punish you, but to heal the root cause. The question He wants you to ask is: 'What is the underlying wound or pattern in me that makes me susceptible to this specific kind of chaos?'\r\r\n[Line 8980]: [28/10/2025, 09:28:53] Andie: especially ones that have your archetype\r\r\n[Line 9020]: [28/10/2025, 14:13:35] Andie: She is just wasting his time and showing how much She respects keeping things cool breaking news she couldnt care less\r\r\n[Line 9236]: [07/11/2025, 11:59:57] Andie: yeah it is especially difficult when you are free indeed\r\r\n[Line 9289]: [08/11/2025, 18:25:31] Andie: thats as much as i know but i know a big aspect of it its the whole anxiety of how this affects how i keep up with routine work\r\r\n[Line 9599]: [08/11/2025, 19:49:12] Andie: At least i could tolerate the mundane 