pect to helpd with it is actually getting referred to the appropriate diatetians / nutrionists too �?Z<This message was edited>\r\r\n[Line 10438]: [21/11/2025, 23:01:38] Andie: Cause it looks like you can only also be under the catchment you live at which is the most bothersome aspect of medical stuff.\r\r\n[Line 10484]: [21/11/2025, 23:22:56] Andie: I think for me is just music and drumming so i am trying to get back into it and not only from that perspective but also building digital tools in that space\r\r\n[Line 10602]: [22/11/2025, 00:11:32] Andie: I just hate being in a state of confusion and neediness of others cause how self sufficient i had to be all these years and also the nature of people just not being as available and especially in this UK system always as understanding\r\r\n[Line 10607]: [22/11/2025, 00:13:25] Andie: Especially cause i know how badly people handled it around tou Oppy\r\r\n[Line 10618]: [22/11/2025, 00:14:55] Andie: and i had been telling u this especially that u werent crazy feeling all some type of way\r\r\n[Line 10628]: [22/11/2025, 00:17:06] Hope: Mimi specifically �Y~' I�?Tm sorry but I was deffo a threat to her\r\r\n[Line 10636]: [22/11/2025, 00:18:47] Andie: I will not stop thinking she is on the spectrum\r\r\n[Line 10637]: [22/11/2025, 00:19:03] Hope: What spectrum �Y~'�Y~'\r\r\n[Line 10638]: [22/11/2025, 00:19:18] Andie: the one and only spectrum\r\r\n[Line 10681]: [22/11/2025, 00:26:37] Andie: Cause respectfully Mimi is a lot\r\r\n[Line 10698]: [22/11/2025, 00:29:58] Andie: To others especially and i promise u ud easily see that in whether people stick around much her\r\r\n[Line 10725]: [22/11/2025, 00:34:04] Andie: But its especially with your friends that u should feel the most honest about them\r\r\n[Line 10736]: [22/11/2025, 00:36:54] Andie: I like that she has found someone like Fizzy but i feel like the only thing that has let Fizzy manage it cause he comes with a reasonable feminine energy about himself so can be very 