raction, you got sth special here Oppy�Y'O\r\r\n[Line 11610]: [04/12/2025, 12:23:58] Hope: It actually put into perspective for example people that get reaped how they may struggle mentally. Thinking everyone knows but that�?Ts not even the case. \r\r\n[Line 11624]: [04/12/2025, 12:28:35] Andie: That people especially with how social our personal one are set up wont have that attitude towards us no?\r\r\n[Line 11677]: [04/12/2025, 12:38:45] Andie: Attracting even more speculations for those subscribed to your life\r\r\n[Line 11735]: [04/12/2025, 13:01:44] Andie: Does the green message-count bubble actually trigger any specific psychological response? And would that effect be the same if the messages were from someone close to you, like your mum or brother, compared to someone else?\r\r\n[Line 11768]: [04/12/2025, 13:10:33] Andie: Since i work at the intersection of thins im trying lean into the conversation especially considering overstimulation\r\r\n[Line 11847]: [04/12/2025, 19:17:49] Andie: The field is immense so having specialists lend opinions brings much needed clarity and lightness\r\r\n[Line 11889]: [04/12/2025, 20:29:05] Andie: But serious humans respect serious humane invitations to also gain personal credit as they did as a clinic today\r\r\n[Line 11891]: [04/12/2025, 20:30:32] Andie: I didnt send u this to pay attention to Jake but to pay attention to Winfrei and how when she was just an hyper ambitious media woman she commanded presence in rooms she didnt belong in and especially had Maya Angelou ask herself, �?owho is this lady�??\r\r\n[Line 12099]: *The Hijack (Capture):* Instead of letting it become an \"open tab,\" you immediately hit the \"Share\" button and send it to a specific note in your notes app called \"Fashion Inspiration\" or a specific Pinterest board. You might add a quick tag like #datenight or #gottamakeit.\r\r\n[Line 12309]: [05/12/2025, 20:03:15] Andie: nothing i just got referred by genomics specialist now\r\r\n[Line 12339]: [05/12/2025, 20:14:51] Andie: and what would deplate it that i do that i don't realise, especially stressors, triggers and bad habits\r\r\n[Line 12354]: [05/12/2025, 20:17:57] Hope: Okay, has fizzy found a job now?\r\r\n[Line 12358]: [05/12/2025, 20:18:29] Andie: and ive been working on GetAway on and off finishing the User Interface relaunch\r\r\n[Line 12367]: [05/12/2025, 20:21:18] Andie: we all have our silos in tech, cause i am a generalist by necessity. he is a speciliast, Python more so and also i feel like he is also has a salary preference\r\r\n[Line 12381]: �?Z[05/12/2025, 20:26:37] Andie: funny times, the hunger was unparalleled. in fact i scroll back at it with immense pride, especially driving USW study skills Generative AI policy before i left. �?Zimage omitted\r\r\n[Line 12389]:  My brain is inefficient. It burns more glucose and oxygen to do the same task as someone else because of that \"uneven profile\" (High Verbal vs Low Memory). I think this is also what causes me to be such an external processor, i talk a lot, it would randomly decompress me, especially if i have a leaning hear, but usually always been the one on the listening side.\r\r\n[Line 12420]: [09/12/2025, 21:12:29] Hope: Fizzy is going through some stuff\r\r\n[Line 12452]: [10/12/2025, 17:24:43] Hope: Fizzy, \r\r\n[Line 12459]: [10/12/2025, 17:42:57] Andie: Yup! I hear that and Fizzy obvs has been a bystander\r\r\n[Line 12635]: [11/12/2025, 14:54:30] Andie: Would love to read it if u have it in any digitally readable format cause i know it would have a big aspect of that building others/ecosystem attitude you come with\r\r\n[Line 12768]: [11/12/2025, 16:32:15] Andie: Cause generationally speaking we live in a very selfish time especially when it comes to the west and its diaspora\r\r\n[Line 12888]: [11/12/2025, 20:10:01] Andie: Then i think you should do that in the context of projects you like or join those gov funded programme that have other people on them but that would be in person cause u know u need that in person aspect. The stem thing i said often already has many of such opportunity built in.\r\r\n[Line 13116]: [17/12/2025, 16:05:08] Andie: I may be low on that self awareness cause definitely i struggle to be in the moment with my body cause obvs i just want to get on with life and sometimes cause i dont get a choice of being able to do so cause at this moment in time im also helping my mum navigate through her recovery. My sister is covering some aspect whereas has ive paid more close attention to what \r\n[Line 13125]: [17/12/2025, 16:09:35] Andie: But thanks what you do keep telling me and stuff you mention here and there do help keep giving me perspective and advocating correctly for myself\r\r\n[Line 13228]: [17/12/2025, 16:40:50] Andie: Whenever i get that question all i can really say is just to keep praying for me and also bearing with me, especially when i am struggling to get across to you frustrations and whatnot.\r\r\n[Line 13354]: [22/12/2025, 15:39:43] Andie: There is this guy in ai that i followed that literally just described how ive felt in some areas obvs his is not adhd per se although he is on the spectrum tho but it literally gosh gave a lot of language to my �?osluggishness�?? u can check his perspective here on chronic stuff: https://substack.com/app-link/post?publication_id=2016047&post_id=182303974&utm_source=po\r\n[Line 13390]: [22/12/2025, 16:41:35] Andie: Guess who reached out today? Fizzy!!! So we catching up in about an hr and Joseph\r\r\n[Line 13426]: [22/12/2025, 16:49:34] Andie: Imaginn me working with Fizzy that knows u\r\r\n[Line 13463]: [22/12/2025, 16:57:27] Andie: It felt like the most straightforward way in, because it enables me to move into salaried, meaningful projects tied to my STEM experience, especially at a time when there is substantial funding circulating in the UK. �?Z<This message was edited>\r\r\n[Line 13528]: [23/12/2025, 16:52:20] Andie: Even when it comes to noticing what others don�?Tt most especially\r\r\n[Line 13798]: [05/01/2026, 19:07:52] Andie: Context is everything cause of the psychology of perspective\r\r\n[Line 13831]: [05/01/2026, 19:16:50] Andie: came in her life within 7 days, he was like, would you marry me? next time around what's ur ring size? couple week later he is at our crib, shortly after he is meeting one of my respected uncle for a further assessment past mine and mother's\r\r\n[Line 13898]: [05/01/2026, 19:34:07] Andie: I'll be raw with you. As a man, and the truth is I could feel this way about a loyal woman, but that does not mean I take it lightly. It only means I recognize the vulnerability she has placed in my hands. She has trusted me with her heart and her future, and that trust demands that I handle her with the utmost care and respect.\r\r\n[Line 14170]: [05/01/2026, 21:04:06] Andie: as you know relationship especially the long comitted ones require the work they require, for validation, confirmation and continuity, so things can be business as usual. BAU.\r\r\n[Line 14222]: [05/01/2026, 21:22:30] Andie: what we resolved in the end that he just as i think you should as well hand on the fact that you met such a career spec and therefore those opportunities may not just present themselves ones.\r\r\n[Line 14232]: [05/01/2026, 21:27:01] Andie: What we ultimately concluded is that, just as I think you should, you should hold onto the fact that you now know this career specification; you can use it to identify and pursue similar opportunities going forward.\r\r\n[Line 14236]: [05/01/2026, 21:28:10] Andie: Because you understand it, you can recognise other opportunities in the future that match these specifications.\r\r\n[Line 14240]: [05/01/2026, 21:29:09] Andie: I know how intense it feels to wait on something like UNIDO, especially when your heart is fully in it. That waiting, the uncertainty. it can really drain your energy and make everything else feel impossible.\r\r\n[Line 14242]: [05/01/2026, 21:29:36] Andie: it�?Ts in the career specification you now understand.\r\r\n[Line 14292]: Gain clarity on your career specifications, which informs future decisions\r\r\n[Line 14360]: [07/01/2026, 10:55:29] Andie: This, this is what it ends up looking when it comes together from a thematic standpoint not specific layout cause that is more Rihanna foundation inspired. Your one.\r\r\n[Line 14771]: [27/01/2026, 14:39:31] Andie: Yeah exactly cause otherwise this is verh mich sending a message thay u Opprah are not to be trusted or i just domt feel that close to even respect tell u why im being like that with u\r\r\n[Line 14786]: [27/01/2026, 14:41:38] Andie: Would natural give u a different perspective to put ur self in their shoes\r\r\n[Line 15094]: [27/01/2026, 17:36:00] Andie: Not just that particularly but we just �?ospecial�?? or whatever that means\r\r\n[Line 15294]: [03/02/2026, 17:51:14] Andie: And also the strong hold stress and ANXIETY especially worrat cocktail ever can have\r\r\n[Line 15300]: [03/02/2026, 17:51:52] Hope: Yeah so if it�?Ts finding a specific job work on that\r\r\n[Line 15426]: [03/02/2026, 20:24:52] Andie: And that just so happens to be a by product of someone who worked on that craft all of their childhood teenage years and had a love and respect for it\r\r\n[Line 16058]: [09/02/2026, 17:37:02] Andie: Yeah talking therapy will help him especially centred person therapy\r\r\n[Line 16072]: [09/02/2026, 17:41:04] Andie: Social dynamics is crazy. Lots of unpacking. But u that can read the room need to know where not to push. And i know u can especially over call not texts.\r\r\n[Line 16126]: [09/02/2026, 18:17:31] Andie: Literally what the cover says, winning the waging war within that pretty much every men in this century especially one like him, Jason, has been teaching now the young black kids from the bronx from early. Cause we do collectively internalise everything and joke about our �?otraumas�??\r\r\n[Line 16168]: [09/02/2026, 18:31:20] Andie: Got a meeting with getaway founders\r\r\n[Line 16203]: [10/02/2026, 18:46:53] Andie: Thats why i suspected this\r\r\n[Line 16277]: [14/02/2026, 17:02:02] Andie: But respectfully i feel certain things be really not just about someone being caring and big time empah but genuinely that their brain is quite literally wired differently and so for it\r\r\n[Line 16278]: [14/02/2026, 17:02:22] Andie: Thanks this helps a lot filtering it especially coming from a boss babe�Y~'\r\r\n[Line 16311]: [14/02/2026, 17:09:51] Andie: Thats how i feel about u, i feel id love to take ur deep thinking brain apart cause the same brain that overthinks is the same one that has just changed someone whole perspective in life in a milliesec\r\r\n[Line 16316]: [14/02/2026, 17:11:54] Andie: Especially around even the simpliest questions cause sometimes when i may be in a space where im not even ready to talk about something\r\r\n[Line 16350]: [14/02/2026, 17:26:08] Andie: U see how u urself are actually speculating a lot cause the panel fine said a whole bunch of predictable stuff and also almost rebuked her but then i feel they still missed it and there should have been more questions about context!!!\r\r\n[Line 16416]: �?Z[17/02/2026, 07:23:22] Andie: Especially her, other story: �?Zimage omitted\r\r\n[Line 16461]: [24/02/2026, 09:49:47] Andie: So taking the approach of say I want to experiment with ideas and launch a product online and gather interest before spending the effort to code it, if I share this with you which aspect of it do you think you�?Td want to emphasise most in a session?\r\r\n[Line 16522]: [28/02/2026, 05:54:49] Hope: Yes, do you have a specific time?\r\r\n[Line 16528]: [01/03/2026, 09:01:13] Andie: I remember shooting with u in treforest trying to capture whatever make up gadget that was mid air�Y~' so i respect the hassle\r\r\n[Line 16751]: [04/03/2026, 01:18:21] Andie: Ill have to give into that a bit, but i thing canva is quite comprehensive especially at the �?oadvanced user�?? level\r\r\n[Line 16841]: [04/03/2026, 19:45:11] Andie: I think you�?Tll really lvoe this especially: https://youtu.be/7pdzyJu9JkI\r\r\n[Line 17020]: [08/03/2026, 18:29:18] Andie: btw Oppy I am even behind. I am still not using fully autonomous agents cause I like to learn and earn the hard stuff. And own aspect of the process.\r\r\n[Line 17047]: [08/03/2026, 19:57:51] Andie: Not our black women being alwsys the honest to be the most ridiculised, disrespected and misold the worst crap:\r\r\n[Line 17230]: [12/03/2026, 19:32:32] Andie: There�?Ts the whole respect to data controller and u know gdpr etc etc\r\r\n[Line 17407]: [18/03/2026, 17:02:23] Andie: Its long been established that any human can only hold up to 7 items roughly in their working memory and for the longest time human especially those competivienly doing memory games find shortcut to �?oindex�?? ur mind to store info and pass info faster to short term then long term memory\r\r\n[Line 17421]: [18/03/2026, 17:06:57] Andie: Its extremely cluttered and in fact from a design perspective it fails User friendly in so many levels but at the same time is a work of hard cause they won across vertical\r\r\n[Line 17567]: [19/03/2026, 07:45:19] Andie: Its definitely gave me perspective also where you was struggling the most and may have just needed to find your comfort but also discomfort to find your comfort again\r\r\n[Line 17601]: [19/03/2026, 15:16:33] Andie: That�?Ts the workflows I am trying to lock in but especially in that particular domain cause i have some knowledge gaps there still its too domain focus so what i know doesnt generalise enough\r\r\n[Line 17691]: [19/03/2026, 17:54:06] Hope: Cause that�?Ts my whole perspective of excel\r\r\n[Line 17736]: [19/03/2026, 18:16:14] Andie: I think you could especially cheat sheet\r\r\n[Line 17768]: [19/03/2026, 18:32:34] Andie: To get up to speed and tell u any specifics\r\r\n[Line 17792]: [19/03/2026, 19:00:58] Andie: apparently we got an inspection our crib tomorrow so its stressing me out cause ive gotta do a bunch of things i was gonna do in the weekend like garden and whatnot\r\r\n[Line 17795]: [19/03/2026, 19:03:49] Hope: Oh lol I was gonna say inspection for what\r\r\n[Line 17828]: [19/03/2026, 19:13:16] Andie: They hygene aspect ive seen that trend a lot in docs\r\r\n[Line 17868]: [19/03/2026, 19:44:35] Andie: Personally im not suprised is a highly specialised industry\r\r\n[Line 17917]: [19/03/2026, 20:01:54] Andie: Also digging more \"Aptitude\" refers to a natural or acquired capacity to learn and execute. u forgeting a specific formula but knows how to find the answer (e.g., using a helper column, combining two simpler formulas, or using the AI/Help feature if permitted), that demonstrates high aptitude. They want to see ur logic, not a robotic memorisation of every Excel functi\r\n[Line 18079]: [20/03/2026, 10:34:52] Andie: \"Excel Tutor\" in the search bar, filter by \"People,\" and review profiles for specific expertise.\r\r\n[Line 18136]: [22/03/2026, 07:17:35] Andie: This raises lots of questions in me�?�about the whole spectrum\r\r\n[Line 18226]: [26/03/2026, 09:41:21] Andie: Please I have a interest based brain, so it makes sense I would on things I somehow care about i still go through a ritual and its painstakingly hard on some days especially on low sleep or when i feel stress in my brain, veines or wherever is comin from. I need to pep talk\r\r\n[Line 18256]: But I somehow i guess with all i read and listened to agree firmly with u that she was grossly misdiagnosed. U can easily map it out by checking the overllaps of what she was diagnosed with with what you suspected being Adhd or that plus commorbities �?Z<This message was edited>\r\r\n[Line 18261]: I do have an exceptionally smart friend i made at uni and her hubby that knows loads about it so will ask them someday. Im sure there�?Ts a lot to learn within that alone, there always is and also move in peer review research which is also helpful in its trial to help you have a grounded perspective\r\r\n[Line 18502]: [26/03/2026, 21:09:52] Andie: Thanks for this cause i felt like a hot mess, i think off late i realise i ruminate a lot and it especially about anything uncertain and there�?Ts been a lot of uncertainty in the past 2 years whjch also means a backdrop of anxiety man is hard to be human in the 21st . Wont ever say we have it harder but its sth �?Z<This message was edited>\r\r\n[Line 18904]: [27/04/2026, 22:45:28] Andie: So specialising in operational agility\r\r\n[Line 18910]: Just lineing up my ducks so that i am prepared when certain things are enforced and i am ready to offer more also via hiring friends and partners really, especially family !!! �?Z<This message was edited>\r\r\n[Line 18960]: [09/05/2026, 11:28:42] Andie: Cause especially as u say when ur on meds u say that ur brain doeant even have time to process limiting emotions like t\r\r\n[Line 18965]: [09/05/2026, 13:06:17] Andie: Oh okay and the meds obvs dont help with this specific neurological side of ur sudden intensity and rigidity\r\r\n[Line 18974]: [09/05/2026, 13:16:19] Andie: Have u left therapy or sought specific grief counselling\r\r\n[Line 19176]: [22/05/2026, 08:46:46] Andie: Sorry haven�?Tt got to all that yet cause all these Charity deals and claims they are a bit long and convoluted and didn�?Tt want to keep coming back to u for more specifics about stuff but get it all at once from you so could just execute. My biggest blocker as been this btw, which also would be the hosting platform of ur site:\r\r\n[Line 19321]: [29/05/2026, 16:09:04] Hope: Ahh, the learning is on the job learning not a specific course I�?Tve personally enrolled myself on �?Z<This message was edited>\r\r\n[Line 19381]: [30/05/2026, 13:09:57] Hope: Did your guy say a specific time?\r\r\n",
